02534276.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gjv1665702534276.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gjv1665702534276.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gjv1665702534276\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns an array of <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.View</span> objects representing the views of a component instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gjv1665702534276__topic_d125720e1_d125721e1_d125722e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gjv1665702534276__p_d125723e1_d125724e1_d125725e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Instance</var>.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getViews()</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gjv1665702534276__section_gt1_1hr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d565234e70\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gjv1665702534276__section_v5d_bhr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d565234e79\">Return Value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"gjv1665702534276__parml_kdk_rgr_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">An array of <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.View</span> objects that represent the views of the\n            specified component instance.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Instance</a><p>The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xbg1665702534713.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.View</a><p>The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView().</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/skz1665702535167.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Multiple Views for Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>A View is an HTML layout that is displayed inside an unbound HTML element in the layout of the web page. Each instance of a dynamic server page (DSP) can have multiple views that provide different layouts for its data.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527882\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527882\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getViews Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 12, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns an array of uniface.View objects representing the views of a component instance. Return = Instance . getViews() Arguments None Return Value Return An array of uniface.View objects that represent the views of the specified component instance. Related Links uniface.Instance The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents. uniface.View The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView(). Multiple Views for Dynamic Server Pages A View is an HTML layout that is displayed inside an unbound HTML element in the layout of the web page. Each instance of a dynamic server page (DSP) can have multiple views that provide different layouts for its data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}